# Cursor Rules (IdeaForge)
# Priority order:
# 1) system/design-docs/PRD.md / ARCHITECTURE.md / DATA_MODEL.md / NFR.md / RUNBOOK.if2.md
# 2) system/design-docs/PRD_VNEXT.md / ARCHITECTURE_VNEXT.md / DATA_MODEL_VNEXT.md / MILESTONES_VNEXT.md (when doing vNext work)
# 3) system/design-docs/AGENTS.md
# 4) system/ai-governance/rules/*.md
#
# Defaults:
# - Plan first, then implement
# - Minimal diffs, no unrelated refactors
# - No secrets; placeholders only
# - Add tests and run validation from RUNBOOK.md and system/design-docs/RUNBOOK.if2.md when doing system-layer work
